¢Ü On a spaceship somewhere ¢Ü

25
00:02:14,467 --> 00:02:21,339
¢Ü Sailing across an empty sea ¢Ü

26
00:02:21,441 --> 00:02:25,138
¢Ü This time tomorrow ¢Ü

27
00:02:25,244 --> 00:02:27,712
¢Ü What will we know? ¢Ü

28
00:02:27,814 --> 00:02:32,148
¢Ü Will we still be here ¢Ü

29
00:02:32,251 --> 00:02:37,848
¢Ü Watching an in-flight
