(train bells dinging)

36
00:03:01,214 --> 00:03:03,910
¢Ü This time tomorrow ¢Ü

37
00:03:04,016 --> 00:03:07,452
¢Ü What will we see? ¢Ü

38
00:03:07,553 --> 00:03:10,386
¢Ü Fields full of houses ¢Ü

39
00:03:10,490 --> 00:03:17,328
¢Ü Endless rows
